RepoPulse Command Center is a cloud-based AI-assisted project intelligence platform designed to provide project managers with actionable visibility into:

Project health
Repository activity
Intern performance
Delivery risk
Team engagement
Operational bottlenecks

The platform integrates with GitHub repositories and analyzes repository activity, project behavior, and historical metrics to provide:

Real-time project insights
Risk indicators
AI-generated recommendations
Team performance visibility
Searchable operational intelligence